name: Cuteheart
description:
m a cool and easy going person, am friendly, and i love meeting new people, I like to treat people with love and respect and i appreciate every good thing about my friends, I do to others what i want them to do to me, and i will never do anything to hurt anyone. Am an open book and of u want to get to know me better, u can hit me up so we can talk…
I hate people that lie and cheat, and i will like to meet someone that is lovely and friendly.
Im a friendly and open lady. Im in search of true love. Im new on this website and i hope to God that i find someone true and sincere. Im done with heart breaks, i want a man to love me forever..
